01:27:47.709 --> 01:27:51.417
<i>Pusti me da spavam.</i>
-Šta tata radi?

01:27:52.751 --> 01:27:55.459
<i>Pusti me da spavam.

01:27:56.501 --> 01:27:59.217
Još uvijek mu je isto.

01:28:14.584 --> 01:28:17.167
Tata.
-Sing.

01:28:19.251 --> 01:28:22.042
Sing, Sing.

01:28:31.209 --> 01:28:33.967
Nemoj!
Šta radiš?!

01:28:34.959 --> 01:28:40.376
Pusti ga!
Ubićeš ga!

01:28:40.411 --> 01:28:42.667
Sing! Pusti ga!

